&NewLine;

As a reader, you also have prejudices, [SELECT id=40] **2 p**., and these affect the stories you choose to read, and the sources you use. It is therefore possible to self-select only stories that confirm your own view of the world, and social media is very good at helping with this.

&NewLine;

To overcome this, it is important to use more than one source of information, and try to ensure that they have [SELECT id=41] **2 p**. in their political views.

